@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home";
}

<!-- Home Page Styling -->
<style>
    .hero-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D2B64 0%, #F8CDDA 100%);
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 150px 10px;
    }

    .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .hero-section p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        background-color: #FFD700;
        color: #1D2B64;
        border: none;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 25px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .features-section {
        padding: 80px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        background: #f4f4f4;
        border-radius: 40px 40px 0 0;
        margin-top: -120px;
    }

    .feature-card {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 25px;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
        color: #222;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #1D2B64;
    }

    .feature-card p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #555;
        margin: 0;
    }
</style>

<div class="hero-section">
    <h1>Welcome to Our Library</h1>
    <p>How about getting to know me before the project?</p>
    <a href="/Home/About" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
</div>

<div class="features-section" id="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Ajda Pekkan Appreciation</h3>
        <p>I'm a fan of Ajda Pekkan too, maybe not as much as Sertan Bozkuş, but still!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Hande Yener Also Deserves Love</h3>
        <p>Even though we may not love her as much as we love Ajda Pekkan, we also like Hande Yener with Sertan Bozkuş!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>AI Over Everything</h3>
        <p>Neither Hande Yener nor Ajda Pekkan – I love AI the most!</p>
    </div>
</div>
